# Ambar-Hub Cursor Rules

## Overview
E-commerce WMS monorepo: NestJS + Next.js 14

## Stack
- pnpm + Turborepo
- Backend: NestJS 10, TypeORM, MySQL (port 3001)
- Frontend: Next.js 14, React 18, TailwindCSS

## Structure
```
apps/api/    → NestJS backend
apps/web/    → Next.js frontend  
packages/    → Shared types
```

## Backend
- Entities extend BaseEntity, snake_case columns
- @InjectRepository for services
- Return { success: true, data }

## Frontend
- page.tsx (server) → PageClient.tsx (client)
- AppLayout needs user={} currentPath=""
- API functions in src/lib/api.ts

## UI: Turkish labels, English code
